Ubukerarugendo mu Rwanda bwinjiza amadovize menshi mu Rwanda kandi byagiye byiyongera ku gipimo cya 25% buri mwaka guhera 2013-18. Urwego rw'ubukerarugendo  rwagize uruhare runini mu kongera ibicuruzwa byoherezwa hanze, Amafaranga yinjije kubera ubukerarugendo muri 2014 ni Miliyoni 305. uru rwego kandi rwakuruye ishoramari ritaziguye ry’amahanga hamwe n’ibicuruzwa mpuzamahanga ,ndetse n'amahoteri menshi yafunguye imiryango  mu gihugu, harimo Marriot, Raddison blue, Park Inn by Raddison, sheraton, Protea, GoldenTulip na Zinc. U Rwanda rurimo gukora nk'ahantu h’ihuriro ry’akarere ndetse n’amahanga, hamwe n’isi nshya - ikigo gisanzwe cy’ibisanzwe, gifite intego yo : kunoza ibikoresho no kwita ku byumba inama ziberamo, korohereza abajya n'abava mu mahanga (gusaba viza kuri interineti, politiki ya viza ku irembo ku Banyafurika bose, politiki imwe ya viza yubukerarugendo kuri EAC), itumanaho riteye imbere. 

'''Ubukerarugendo mu Rwanda''' buriyongera cyane.  Kugira ngo u Rwanda rushyire ku ikarita y’isi nk’icyerekezo cya mbere cy’ubukerarugendo, Ikigo cy’iterambere ry’u Rwanda (RDB) cyasinyanye amasezerano y’ubufatanye n’imyaka itatu n’ikipe y’umupira wamaguru ikorera mu mujyi wa London, Arsenal Football Club ndetse n’ubufatanye bw’imyaka ibiri n’Ikipe yumupira wamaguru ya Paris Saint Germain yo mu Bufaransa kugirango ifashe kubaka ubukerarugendo bwigihugu. Abayobozi b'u Rwanda bavuga ko ibi byazamuye umubare rusange w'ubukerarugendo ku gipimo cya 8%. 

== Ubukerarugendo bwo mu gasozi ==
[[File:A_tourism_car_-_Akagera_National_Park.jpg|thumb| Kuzenguruka muri [[Pariki y'Akagera|Parike y'igihugu ya Akagera]]]]
[[Rwanda|U Rwanda]] ruherereye muri Afurika y'Iburasirazuba kandi rufite amateka menshi n'ubwiza nyaburanga. [[Abakerarugendo]] bazenguruka bayobowe numuyobozi ufite uburambe kabuhariwe mu kwigisha abandi ibijyanye n’imiterere n’ibinyabuzima byo mu [[Rwanda]] . Ingendo zibanda mu gusura  [[Ikirunga|ibirunga]], amasumo n’amashyamba yimvura [[Afurika|atuwe]] ninyamaswa nyinshi zitandukanye zo [[Afurika|muri Afrika]] .

U Rwanda rutuwe n’inyamaswa nini zitandukanye zirimo [[Ingagi zo mu birunga|ingagi zo mu misozi]] ndetse na parike nini ku isi ya hippos - izigera ku 20.000 ni zo zikekwa ko zihari. Nubwo u Rwanda rukiri igihugu kiri mu nzira y'amajyambere, rufite amahoteri atari make kandi inyungu mpuzamahanga nshya mu bukerarugendo zifasha igihugu kuzamuka mu bukungu.

Imifuka ya plastiki irabujijwe mu Rwanda, kandi ba mukerarugendo basabwa kutayizana mu gihugu.

== Ibikurura ba mukerarugendo ==

=== [[Pariki y’Igihugu y’Ibirunga|Parike y'Ibirunga]] ===
[[File:Mother_and_baby_mountain_gorillas._Volcanoes_National_Park,_Rwanda_(8159411404).jpg|thumb|  Ingagi n'umwana wayo muri parike y'ibirunga]]
Muri [[Pariki]] y’ibirunga niho [[ingagi]] zose zo mu Rwanda wazisanga. Kugerayo ni hafi amasaha 2 uvuye kukibuga cyindege mpuzamahanga cya Kigali bituma iyi parike yigihugu yingagi ibarirwa mu zoroshye cyane gusura kurusha izindi kwisi. Iyi pariki y'igihugu mu Rwanda iherereye ku mupaka wa [[Uganda]] ndetse na [[Repubulika Iharanira Demokarasi ya Kongo]],  ibamo umubare munini w'ingagi zo mu misozi zibangamiwe cyane. Abahanga bavuga ko muri iyi parike harimo ingagi zigera kuri 600 - zikaba zariyongereye ziva kuri 240 zigera 250 mu 1981.  Usibye ingagi, Parike y’ibirunga ibamo [[inguge]], [[Inyoni zo mu Rwanda|inyoni]] zitandukanye, ibikururanda, amphibian, nutundi dukoko twinshi bihuriza hamwe bigakora  Safari yuzuye.  Pariki y’ibirunga yitiriwe uruhererekane rw’ibirunga bisinziriye bigizwe na: Karisimbi - iri hejuru cyane kuri metero 4507, Bisoke hamwe n’ikiyaga cyacyo cyiza cyane, Sabinyo, Gahinga na Muhabura. 

Nta gushidikanya, kimwe mu bintu bishimishije gukora mu Rwanda ni '''ukujya gusura ingagi''' '''mu ibirunga .''' Gukora urugendo bimara hagati yamasaha ane nunani ahanini hagendwa namaguru mumashyamba yimigano y'amayobera, inzuri zo mwishyamba, hamwe n’ibishanga. Abayobora muri parike yigihugu barakujyana bakakugeza aho '''imiryango y'ingagi ituye .''' Uhamara isaha imwe witegereza uko ibyo biremwa birya, byiita kubana babyo, nuko bisabana.

=== [[Pariki ya Nyungwe]] ===
Ni imwe mu mashyamba ya kera y’imvura muri Afurika, Nyungwe ni nziza cyane kandi ikungahaye ku binyabuzima bifite amoko 1068 y’ibimera na orchide 140, amoko 322 y’inyoni zirimo Babbler itukura, hamwe n’inyamabere 75 nk'injangwe , mongoose, congo clawless otter, ingwe nibindi. Ba mukerarugendo benshi baza muri iri shyamba ryimvura '''kureba chimpanzees''', hamwe nandi moko 12 y’ibinyabuzima, harimo n’inguge ya L'Hoest iboneka kuri Albertine Rift. Iyi pariki kandi niyo yonyine irimo ikiraro cyo mukirere cyo gutemberamo  '''muri Afurika y'Iburasirazuba''', ni urugendo rw'iminota 90 uvuye mu kigo cyabashyitsi cya Uwinka. Unyura hejuru '''yikiraro cya metero 91 z'uburebure''' gihagarara hejuru ya metero zirenga 50 hejuru yishyamba ryimvura ryinshi, ukabona ibiti n'imisozi biri kure. 

=== [[Pariki ya Akagera]] ===
Urugendo rwo muri Afrika ntirwaba rwuzuye hatarimo gutwara imodoka ureba ibyiza nyaburanga. Ba mukerarugendo bashobora kujya muri safari muri Parike y'igihugu ya Akagera ni '''amasaha abiri n'igice gusa uvuye i Kigali'''. Iyi Pariki icungwa n’umuryango nyafurika wita ku mapariki, iherereye muburasirazuba bwu Rwanda ifite kilometero kare 2500 zumukenke (ni imwe muzifite icyanya kinini muri Afurika yo hagati irinzwe). Iyi parike yitiriwe umugezi wa Kagera unyura ku rubibi rw'u Rwanda na Tanzaniya. Umugezi unyura mu kiyaga cya Ihema no mu bindi biyaga bito muri parike no hafi yayo. Iyi pariki igizwe n'ubuso bw'umukenke, iminyinya ibihuru ,ifite ibyatsi byimeza n'ibiyaga icumi byo mu bishanga. Irimo [[inzovu]], imbogo, giraffe, imparage, ingwe, impyisi, [[intare]], [[Impara|impala]] nyinshi nk'ibihuru, Topis, Oribis, water-buck, roan antelope na duiker, klipspringer, impala n' impalage nini ku isi yitwa Cape eland. Ushobora kureba aho imvubu ziteranira naho ingona za [[Nili]] zota izuba hafi yikiyaga cy' Ihema. Ibinyabuzima wasanga muri parike yigihugu ya Akagera ni ibiti bya elayo , inkende za Vervet, inkende z'ubururu. Uzabona ibidukikije kuva mubibaya by'umukenke kugera mu bishanga no mu biyaga byirimo amoko yinyoni 500 n'imparage. 

=== Ikiyaga cya Kivu ===
Ikiyaga cya Kivu gifite ubuso bwa km kare 2 2700,  nicyo kiyaga kinini mu Rwanda kandi kikaba icya gatandatu kinini muri [[Afurika]].  Imisozi ihanamye, itera amaterasi igana ku nkombe nziza y’ikiyaga, hamwe n’imijyi itatu y’ibiruhuko - Gisenyi, Kibuye na Cyangugu.   Ikiyaga cya Kivu gifite amazi meza, ikombe z'umusenyi, hamwe na resitora nziza.

Ku bakora ingendo zidasanzwe, inzira ishimishije yo gutembera  u Rwanda ni urugendo rwo mu bwato ku kiyaga cya Kivu, cyangwa gutwara amagare ku misozi cyangwa gutembera kimwe mu byiciro 6 bitanyuze mu nzira nyabagendwa ya Kongo Nil. 

=== Inzu Ndangamurage y'umwami ===
Niba gusura ibidukikije nyaburanga bitakunyuze cyangwa ngo bikwemeze ko Abanyarwanda bubaha inyamaswa, gusura inzu ndangamurage y’umwami byanze bikunze bizakunyura. kimwe mu bikurura abantu cyane mu inzu ndangamurage (imwe mu '''ngoro ndangamurage umunani zo mu Rwanda''' ) ni [[INYAMBO|inyambo]] n'amahembe manini atangaje. Umunsi wose, '''abaririmbyi gakondo bavugira inka''' mu mivugo - umuhango wihariye u Rwanda.

Inzu ndangamurage ubwayo irashimishije. Yerekana uko ingoro yumwami yari imeze kuva mu kinyejana cya 15 ifite igisenge kibisi, inzu ya cyami, inzu nzizabatunganyirizagamo amata gakondo yakorwaga n’umugore utarashatse.

Ba mukerarugendo bashobora kandi gusura inzu yubukoroni yahoze ari '''iy'umwami Mutara III Rudahigwa''' hagati mukinyejana cya 20. Igishushanyo mbonera cy'imbere kiratangaje cyane, gihuza imiterere y'u Rwanda n'ibikoresho byo mu Burayi (bimwe muri byo byari iby'umwami). 

=== [[Inzu Ndangamurage]] ===
Kimwe mu '''byegeranyo byiza''' bya Afurika '''by’ibintu by'ubukorikori by’amoko atandukanye bya kera''' mushobora kubisanga mu nzu ndangamurage y’u Rwanda, iherereye mu birometero 130 mu majyepfo ya '''Kigali''' mu karere ka '''[[Akarere ka Huye|Huye]].''' [[Ububiligi]] bwahaye inzu ndangamurage uyu mujyi mu 1989 mu rwego rwo kwizihiza isabukuru yimyaka 25 u Rwanda rwigenga.

Ingoro ndangamurage ya Ethnographic ifite uduce turindwi twereka ba mukerarugendo igihe cyu Rwanda rwabakoloni. Haboneka kandi icyegeranyo gishimishije cyibiseke byaboshywe, imyenda gakondo ikozwe mu mpu zinyamaswa n’ibyatsi biboshye, amacumu n'imiheto, ingoma z'umuziki zo mu binyejana byashize, n'ibikoresho byo guhinga bishaje.

Ba mukerarugendo bashobora kwinjira munzu yumwami ya nyayo bakamenya uko yubatswe. Inzu ndangamurage kandi yakira '''imyiyerekano yubukorikori.''' 

=== Urwibutso rwa Jenoside yakorewe abatutsi rwa Kigali ===
Abaturage b'u Rwanda biyemeje kwimakaza amahoro n'ubwiyunge. Biyemeje kurwanya ingengabitekerezo ya jenoside. Inzibutso zubatse mu gihugu hose zegeranyije ubuhamya mu kwibuka abazize Jenoside yakorewe Abatutsi.

Urwibutso rwa Jenosideyakorewe abatutsi rwa Kigali ku Gisozi rwatangijwe ku isabukuru yimyaka 10 jenoside yakorewe abatutsi ibaye, hashyinguwe 250.000. Uru rwibutso kandi rugira uruhare mu kwigisha uburyo Itsembabwoko ryakorewe abatutsi ryakozwe kandi risuzuma jenoside mu kinyejana cya 20.

Urukuta ruriho amazina y'abazize jenoside yakorewe abatutsi kandi ni umurimo ugikomeza. Amazina menshi ntarakusanyirizwa hamwe ngo yandikwe kandi benshi mubazize jenoside baruhukiye mu mva amazina yabo ntaramenyekana.

Ubusitani bw'urwibutso butanga umwanya wo gutekereza bucece ku mateka ya Jenoside yakorewe abatutsi. Bemerera abashyitsi gutekereza uburyo twese dufite inshingano zacu zo gukumira ivangura nubugizi bwa nabi. Mu gihe urwibutso runini ruri i Kigali, itsembabwoko ryakorewe abatutsi  ryakozwe mu Rwanda hose, hari inzibutso mu bice bitandukanye mu gihugu hose. 

